\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}One or two paragraphs of verbiage and at least one image. \
{\listtext	\'95	}Best practices for writing articles:
\i  \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural
\ls1\ilvl1\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}
\i0\b Use Lists or Bullet Points 
\b0 - Articles presented in the form of a list or bulleted points are proven to increase audience engagement and click-through rate.\
\ls1\ilvl1
\i {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}
\i0\b How-to\'92s
\b0  - Teach your audience something by writing a concise, step-by-step process article (e.g. 
\i How to
\i0  prune forsythia)\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural
\ls1\ilvl1
\b \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8259 	}Top # Lists 
\b0 - This type of post also garners a higher click-though rate with social media audiences. (e.g. Top 3 Places to Spot Warblers at Morris Arboretum)
\i \
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural

